diff --git a/issue_onboarding_status.txt b/issue_onboarding_status.txt
new file mode 100644
index 000000000..ced7bfd5c
--- /dev/null
+++ b/issue_onboarding_status.txt
@@ -0,0 +1 @@
+Issue: after POST /v1/accounts/onboard Torii returns tx_hash_hex, but GET /v1/pipeline/transactions/status?hash=<tx_hash_hex> always returns 404. This path is not present in the Torii OpenAPI, yet both mobile SDKs (Swift and Android) poll it, so onboarding never reaches a terminal status. We need either this endpoint restored or a documented status-check method (e.g., SSE /v1/events/sse) plus SDK updates.
-- 
